ADD utopia.1.name:0 "A Request for the [ringworld_builder.GetName]"
CN2 utopia.1.name:0 "对 [ringworld_builder.GetName] 的请求"
ADD utopia.1.desc.v1:0 "Some of our intelligence assets have uncovered data suggesting that the [ringworld_builder.GetName]'s ring world could be hiding a secret launch platform for weapons of mass destruction. Though the validity of the source has yet to be confirmed, the notion has taken hold with the public who demand that we take action. Surely if the [ringworld_builder.GetName] has nothing to hide, they will allow a team of our weapons experts to inspect the site."
CN2 utopia.1.desc.v1:0 "我们的情报部门发现 [ringworld_builder.GetName] 的星环世界可能藏匿着大规模杀伤性武器的发射平台。尽管情报来源的可靠性亟待确认，但是公众中要求就此事采取行动的观念已经占据了主流。如果 [ringworld_builder.GetName] 问心无愧的话，他们理应允许我们的武器专家团队前往检查。"
ADD utopia.1.desc.v2:0 "Since the [ringworld_builder.GetName] started construction on a ring world, several of our leading engineers have been following the project from afar, and are greatly impressed with their progress. They believe we could learn from studying their craftsmanship closer, and suggest that we ask their permission to station a research team on location."
CN2 utopia.1.desc.v2:0 " [ringworld_builder.GetName] 正在着力建造一个星环世界，我们的几位首席工程师也一直在远距离跟进该项目，并且对于他们所取得的进展深感震撼。工程师们认为近距离观摩对方的建筑工程将会让他们受益良多，因此希望我们向对方请求派出一支考察队。"
ADD utopia.1.desc.v4:0 "Lately prophets across the empire have been plagued by horrific visions of death and destruction, tied to the appearance of a great circular object in the sky. Putting two and two together, our religious leaders are worried that the [ringworld_builder.GetName]'s ambition to build a ring world has angered the gods, and advise us to send a delegation to consecrate the project, before it's too late."
CN2 utopia.1.desc.v4:0 "最近，整个帝国的先知们都看到了死亡和毁灭的恐怖幻象，是跟天空中出现的一个圆形物体有关的。宗教领袖们担心是 [ringworld_builder.GetName] 企图建造一个星环世界的野心激怒了神明，所以建议我们派一名代表去给这项工程祈福，以防止幻象中的情景变成现实。"
ADD utopia.1.a:0 "Forward our request to the [ringworld_builder.GetName]."
CN2 utopia.1.a:0 "将我们的要求告知 [ringworld_builder.GetName] 。"
ADD utopia.1.b:0 "That's out of the question."
CN2 utopia.1.b:0 "没门，这事没得商量。"
ADD utopia.1.b.tooltip:1 "Adds the §YMegastructure Demands Rejected§! modifier to affected Pops:\n£happiness£ Happiness §R-20%§!"
CN2 utopia.1.b.tooltip:1 "受影响人口将添加§Y拒绝巨构建筑请求§!的修正：\n\n£happiness幸福度§R-20%§!"
ADD utopia.2.name:0 "A Request from the [From.From.GetName]"
CN2 utopia.2.name:0 "来自 [From.From.GetName] 的请求"
ADD utopia.2.a:0 "Accept the request."
CN2 utopia.2.a:0 "接受请求。"
ADD utopia.2.a.tooltip:0 "This will please the [From.From.GetName]."
CN2 utopia.2.a.tooltip:0 "此事会取悦 [From.From.GetName] 。"
ADD utopia.2.b:0 "Deny the request."
CN2 utopia.2.b:0 "拒绝请求。"
ADD utopia.2.b.tooltip:0 "This will upset the [From.From.GetName]."
CN2 utopia.2.b.tooltip:0 "此事会惹恼 [From.From.GetName] 。"
ADD utopia.2.c:0 "It would be an honor."
CN2 utopia.2.c:0 "这是我们的荣幸。"
ADD utopia.2.desc.v1:0 "The [From.From.GetName] claims to have uncovered intel suggesting that we are building a secret launch platform for weapons of mass-destruction on our ring world and requests our permission to inspect the site.\n\nOur military advisers have yet to confirm whether it's an honest mistake or something more sinister. Either way we should handle the situation delicately."
CN2 utopia.2.desc.v1:0 " [From.From.GetName] 说他们发现我们正在星环世界秘密建造大规模杀伤性武器的发射平台，他们想去那里进行调查，希望获得我们的批准。我们的军事顾问目前还不确定这到底是他们无心的误会还是他们的某种阴谋。不管如何，我们必须小心应对。"
ADD utopia.2.desc.v2:0 "Engineers from the [From.From.GetName] have been following the construction of our ring world from afar, and are greatly impressed with our progress. They request our permission to station a team of engineers there to learn from our efforts."
CN2 utopia.2.desc.v2:0 " [From.From.GetName] 的工程师正在远方密切关注我们的星环世界的建设情况，他们对我们的进度感到十分满意。他们希望我们能批准他们派遣一队工程师到现场来观摩我们的建筑过程。"
ADD utopia.2.desc.v4:0 "Lately prophets from the [From.From.GetName] have been plagued by horrific visions of death and destruction, tied to the appearance of a great circular object in the sky. Worried that the unsanctioned construction of a ring world in our empire has angered the gods, they ask our permission to consecrate it, before we finalize the project."
CN2 utopia.2.desc.v4:0 "最近， [From.From.GetName] 的先知们都看到了死亡和毁灭的恐怖幻象，是跟天空中出现的一个圆形物体有关的。他们担心在帝国未经批准就建设的星环世界可能会激怒神明，因此他们打算在工程完成之前对其进行祈福，希望得到我们的批准。"
ADD utopia.3.name:0 "Request Accepted"
CN2 utopia.3.name:0 "请求被接受"
ADD utopia.3.desc.v1:0 "In good faith, the [From.GetName] has agreed to let a team of our weapons experts search their ring world for a hidden launch platform. A selection of our most qualified specialists are already headed to the site. Soon we will know the truth."
CN2 utopia.3.desc.v1:0 "为了保持和我们的友好关系， [From.GetName] 答应让我们派一队武器专家去他们的星环世界那里调查下是否有秘密的武器发射平台。我们派出了一批最顶尖的专家赶赴现场，我们很快就能得悉真相。"
ADD utopia.3.desc.v2:0 "To the excitement of the scientific community, we have received word that the [From.GetName] would be honored to host a team of our researchers on their ring world. The engineering chief has organized to send a delegation of our finest engineers there shortly, to report on the construction process."
CN2 utopia.3.desc.v2:0 " [From.GetName] 发出声明表示很乐意让我们派一批研究员去星环世界考察，科学界对这个消息感到十分惊喜。首席工程师安排了一支由最优秀的工程师所组成的代表团前往考察该工程的进度。"
ADD utopia.3.desc.v4:0 "The [From.GetName] welcomes our efforts to align with a higher presence, and promises to halt all construction on the ring world till our religious leaders are satisfied that it won't interfere with divine will.\n\nA handful of chosen officials are setting out for the construction site immediately, to ensure that the grim prophecy is never fulfilled."
CN2 utopia.3.desc.v4:0 " [From.GetName] 对我们的要求十分重视，他们承诺会立刻中止星环世界的所有工程建设，直到我们的宗教统治者认为其工程不会违逆天意为止。一批精心挑选的宗教代表正赶赴工程现场，以确保该灾难性预言不会应验。"
ADD utopia.3.a:0 "Excellent."
CN2 utopia.3.a:0 "棒极了。"
ADD utopia.4.name:0 "Request Denied."
CN2 utopia.4.name:0 "请求被拒绝。"
ADD utopia.4.desc:0 "Unfortunately the [From.GetName] did not agree to our terms, worsening the relations between our empires."
CN2 utopia.4.desc:0 " [From.GetName] 并没有答应我们的要求，此举让我们两国之间的关系恶化。"
ADD utopia.4.a:0 "A shame."
CN2 utopia.4.a:0 "太可惜了。"
ADD utopia.5.name:0 "Mission Complete"
CN2 utopia.5.name:0 "任务完成"
ADD utopia.5.desc.v1:0 "The experts sent to inspect the [From.GetSpeciesName] ring world have scoured the construction site for a secret launch platform, yet found nothing to back our claims. We can only conclude that our intelligence was faulty, and review our sources more carefully the next time."
CN2 utopia.5.desc.v1:0 "派去调查 [From.GetSpeciesName] 星环世界的武器专家们到处寻找秘密的武器发射平台，但却一无所获。此事只能断定是我们的情报来源出了问题，下次必须更加仔细地分析情报才行。"
ADD utopia.5.desc.v2:0 "The researchers we sent to the [From.GetSpeciesName] ring world have returned with new knowledge within the field of engineering. Despite some initial misunderstandings due to cultural differences, both teams were satisfied with the exchange and have learned much from each other."
CN2 utopia.5.desc.v2:0 "派去 [From.GetSpeciesName] 的星环世界进行考察的研究员们学到了一些工程领域的新知识。尽管一开始双方由于文化方面的差异而有一些交流上的障碍，但最终还是进行了充分的交流，双方都颇有收获。"
ADD utopia.5.desc.v4:0 "The religious officials sent to consecrate the [From.GetName]'s ring world, have returned from their mission with more questions than answers. As they meditated on the construction platform, they entered a deep divinatory trance, and discovered that the ring world is not the cause of the visions after all. Though unable to decipher the true meaning of the visions, they reassure us that "what may be, may never be...""
CN2 utopia.5.desc.v4:0 "派去 [From.GetName] 星环世界进行祈福的宗教人员现在已经返回，但他们却带回了更多的疑问。当他们在工程建设现场进行冥想时，他们跟神明进行了深度的交流，发现星环世界并非之前那个灾难预言的诱因。虽然还无法确认这道信息的真意，不过可以确定的是“可能发生的事情，可能永远都不会发生……”"
ADD utopia.5.b:0 "Excellent."
CN2 utopia.5.b:0 "棒极了。"
ADD utopia.6.name:0 "Ring World Request: Conclusion"
CN2 utopia.6.name:0 "星环世界请求：结论"
ADD utopia.6.desc.v1:0 "After picking half the construction site apart, the weapons experts from the [From.From.GetName] finally had to concede that there is no secret weapons launch platform on our ring world. An effort we could have spared them, if only they had trusted us..."
CN2 utopia.6.desc.v1:0 "从 [From.From.GetName] 派来的武器专家们把星环世界大半个工程现场都翻了个遍，最后得出结论：我们的星环世界根本没有什么秘密武器发射平台。其实如果他们信任我们的话，本来不用这么大费周章的……"
ADD utopia.6.desc.v2:0 "After spending several weeks on the ring world, the engineers from [From.From.GetName] have now left. Despite their cultural differences, both teams were satisfied with the exchange and have learned much from each other."
CN2 utopia.6.desc.v2:0 "从 [From.From.GetName] 派来的工程师们在星环世界逗留了几周后就离开了，虽然彼此之间有很多文化差异，双方之间还是进行了充分的交流，最后大家都收获良多，感到非常满意。"
ADD utopia.6.desc.v4:0 "As they were meditating on the ring world construction platform, the religious leaders from the [From.From.GetName] claim they entered a deep divinatory trance, during which they discovered that the ring world is not the cause of the ominous visions after all. Though unwilling to give a final answer on the true meaning of the visions, they left us with the comforting notion that "what may be, may never be..."\n\nThankfully construction can now begin again."
CN2 utopia.6.desc.v4:0 "来自 [From.From.GetName] 的宗教统治者们在我们星环世界的建筑工程平台上进行了冥想，据他们所说，他们跟神明进行了深度的交流，发现星环世界并非之前那个灾难预言的诱因。虽然他们不愿意透露这道信息的真意，但他们向我们保证“可能发生的事情，可能永远都不会发生……”谢天谢地，建筑工程终于可以继续了。"
ADD utopia.21.name:0 "Favorable Conditions"
CN2 utopia.21.name:0 "优越条件"
ADD utopia.21.desc:0 "Under the skillful leadership of the ring world construction manager, we have been able to optimize the construction workflow, increasing the build speed significantly."
CN2 utopia.21.desc:0 "在星环世界的工程建设总监的出色领导之下，我们充分调动了工程建设所需的人力资源，大大加快了建设速度。"
ADD utopia.22.name:0 "Mineral Deposit"
CN2 utopia.22.name:0 "矿物储藏"
ADD utopia.22.desc:0 "The construction team on the ring world has discovered a large deposit of minerals embedded in extremely porous stone, that will disintegrate during the build process. Though sensitive, the sample could be valuable enough that it would be worth our while to halt construction to extract it."
CN2 utopia.22.desc:0 "星环世界的建筑工程队在超大型多孔石中发现了大量的矿物储藏，而如果继续进行工程建设的话，这个多孔石就会解体。因此，我们需要暂停工程，先将里面珍贵的矿物提取出来。"
ADD utopia.22.a:0 "Extract the deposit."
CN2 utopia.22.a:0 "提取珍贵矿藏。"
ADD utopia.22.b:0 "We can't delay construction."
CN2 utopia.22.b:0 "我们不能让工程延期。"
ADD utopia.27.name:0 "Missing Workers"
CN2 utopia.27.name:0 "工人失踪"
ADD utopia.27.desc:0 "Since construction on the ring world began, a number of workers have gone missing. Though it's likely they've simply left with one of the many transports without notifying their supervisors, we are launching an investigation into their whereabouts. Sadly their unexpected departure has delayed construction slightly."
CN2 utopia.27.desc:0 "自从星环世界的工程建设开始后，许多工人就莫名其妙的失踪了，虽然他们很可能是在没有通知主管的情况下就坐飞船离开了，但我们还是针对此事进行了调查，这些工人的不告而别让工程建设稍微延期了。"
ADD utopia.27.a:0 "That's unfortunate."
CN2 utopia.27.a:0 "太可惜了。"
ADD utopia.28.name:0 "Missing Workers"
CN2 utopia.28.name:0 "工人失踪"
ADD utopia.28.desc:0 "With the arrival of replacement workers, construction on the ring world is finally back on track. Regrettably we have still not been able to locate the missing workers, whose families have now been notified."
CN2 utopia.28.desc:0 "替补工人已经抵达工地，星环世界的工程建设也可以回到正轨了，很遗憾的是我们还是没能找到那些失踪的工人，我们已经通知了那些失踪工人的家属。"
ADD utopia.28.a:0 "Our thoughts are with them."
CN2 utopia.28.a:0 "为他们默哀。"
ADD utopia.23.name:0 "Ring World Pets"
CN2 utopia.23.name:0 "星环世界宠物"
ADD utopia.23.desc:0 "It appears as if one of the planets used to construct the ring world was not as uninhabited as we first thought. A seemingly harmless, but previously unknown species of giant space worm, nicknamed "Coo-coo" after its call, has been transferred to the ring world with fragments from its homeworld.\n\nWith their fuzzy fur and gentle demeanor, the endearing creatures have become an instant favorite with the workers, who are far away from their families and often very lonely. Especially in the light of their missing co-workers.\n\nWe could allow the creatures to continue their lives in peace, or purge them, delaying construction slightly."
CN2 utopia.23.desc:0 "某颗用于建造星环世界的行星原来并非是我们想象中的没有任何生命体。一种闻所未闻，但表面上看起来人畜无害、绰号“库库”的巨型太空蠕虫种族就通过我们搬运自该行星的碎片迁移到了星环世界上。它们皮毛柔软，性情温和，因此很快就成为了工人们的玩伴。这些远离家人的建筑工人们十分孤独，而这些太空蠕虫正好弥补了员工们的失踪同僚的位置。\n\n我们可以让这些太空蠕虫继续平静的生活，也可以选择清除掉它们，但清除它们的过程会稍微延缓工程建设的进度。"
ADD utopia.23.a:0 "Exterminate them."
CN2 utopia.23.a:0 "清除掉它们。"
ADD utopia.23.b:0 "Better not disturb them."
CN2 utopia.23.b:0 "还是不要打扰它们好了。"
ADD utopia.25.name:0 "A Shocking Revelation"
CN2 utopia.25.name:0 "一个令人震惊的发现"
ADD utopia.25.desc:0 "To everyone's amazement, the ring world has erupted into a flurry of color as thousands of space worms, or as it seems, larvae, are transforming into butterflies. Likely the change has been brought on by the generation of an atmosphere.\n\nUnfortunately, celebrations have been cut short by the discovery of a subterranean network of tunnels, in which Coo-coos were caught feeding off the remains of several missing workers.\n\nConstruction has been halted till the creatures have been exterminated, but we expect swift results as the workers are highly motivated. The true nature of the Coo-coo has been revealed."
CN2 utopia.25.desc:0 "让每个人都没想到的是，星环世界的数千个太空蠕虫在一瞬间都变成了蝴蝶翩翩起舞，将整个星环世界笼罩在万紫千红之下。这种变化可能是因为大气层的产生所导致。大家还没来得及庆祝，就发现了一件更让人震惊的事，在错综复杂的地下隧道中，有人发现库库正在吞食失踪工人的遗骸。工程建设立刻中止，大家纷纷投入到消灭太空蠕虫的工作中。为了给死去的工友复仇，工人们格外的卖力，这些危险的生物应该很快会被消灭干净。真是知虫知面不知心，大家终于发现了表面温顺的库库的真实本性。"
ADD utopia.25.a:0 "Good riddance."
CN2 utopia.25.a:0 "总算甩掉麻烦了。"
ADD utopia.26.name:0 "A Shocking Revelation"
CN2 utopia.26.name:0 "一个令人震惊的发现"
ADD utopia.26.desc:0 "The extermination team's efforts to rid the ring world of the giant space worms known as Coo-coos, have been aggravated by violent protests from the construction workers.\n\nIn a desperate attempt to hide his pet, one young man even ventured far enough outside the build site, that he stumbled upon a subterranean network of freshly dug tunnels, where he caught several Coo-coos feeding off the remains of his missing co-workers. After narrowly escaping from his beloved pet, as it tried to spray him with digestive fluids, he alerted the extermination team, which has made short work of the carnivorous worms.\n\nAnd so the true nature of the Coo-coo has finally been revealed."
CN2 utopia.26.desc:0 "为了消灭星环世界上的所有被称为“库库”的太空蠕虫，我们专门成立了一支清理队伍，但清理队伍的工作却受到了建筑工人们的阻挠。为了保护自己的宠物库库，有一个年轻人甚至跑到了工程场地的外围，他在那里发现了一条最近新挖的地下隧道，在隧道中他看到有几个库库正在吞食失踪工人的遗骸。库库们发现他后，立刻用酸液进行攻击。侥幸逃生的年轻人立刻通知了清理队，清除库库的工作终于得以顺利的进行。至此，大家终于发现了表面温顺的库库的真实本性。"
ADD utopia.26.a:0 "What a grisly turn of events."
CN2 utopia.26.a:0 "这反转真是太惊人了。"
ADD utopia.30.name:0 "The One-Eyed Wanderer"
CN2 utopia.30.name:0 "独眼游荡者"
ADD utopia.30.desc.v1:0 "Our empire has been shaken by the discovery that the [dysonsphere_builder.GetName] are building a Dyson Sphere around [dyson_system.GetName], a central star in one of our most beloved constellations, the "One-eyed Wanderer," completely blocking its light.\n\nThe Wanderer, with her single eye, has watched over our kind since the beginning of time, and legend has it that she guides not only our fleets, but the stars themselves in their journey across the sky. And now the [dysonsphere_builder.GetName], in their blatant ignorance, have built a sphere around her eye, blinding her.\n\nThough it will take many years before we can tell a difference from here, our people are crushed that she will no longer be watching over future generations."
CN2 utopia.30.desc.v1:0 "我国最近发现 [dysonsphere_builder.GetName] 正在 [dyson_system.GetName] 这颗中央恒星附近建造一个戴森球，该恒星是我们最重视的星座“独眼游荡者”的其中一颗星，而现在却被戴森球彻底遮挡住了光芒。此举让我们整个帝国为之震惊。独眼游荡者星座一直在守护着我们，传说中它的光芒不但引导着我们的舰队航行，而且还指引着众恒星在星系中的移动。没想到现在 [dysonsphere_builder.GetName] 竟敢用戴森球来遮挡住游荡者的视野。尽管我们的人民还要若干年后才能彻底看不到游荡者的光芒，但大家在得知游荡者将无法继续守望我们的下一代时，都感到痛不欲生。"
ADD utopia.30.a:0 "We deserve a formal apology."
CN2 utopia.30.a:0 "必须向我们郑重道歉。"
ADD utopia.30.b:0 "A donation of 1000 credits could alleviate the pain."
CN2 utopia.30.b:0 "1000能源的捐献应该能减缓我们人民所受到的伤痛。"
ADD utopia.30.c:0 "Maintaining good relations with our neighbors comes first."
CN2 utopia.30.c:0 "和我们邻国之间的友好关系更为重要。"
ADD utopia.31.name:0 "The One-Eyed Wanderer"
CN2 utopia.31.name:0 "独眼游荡者"
ADD utopia.31.intro:0 "We have discovered that you are building a Dyson Sphere around a central star in one of our most beloved constellations, the One-eyed Wanderer.\n\nThe Wanderer has watched over our kind since the beginning of time. With her single eye, she guides not only our fleets, but the stars themselves in their journey across the sky, and now you have built a sphere around it, blinding her."
CN2 utopia.31.intro:0 "我们发现你们正在我们最珍贵的星座“独眼游荡者”的中央恒星附近建造戴森球。独眼游荡者星座一直在守护着我方，她的光芒不但指引着我们的舰队，还引导着星系中的诸多恒星，而你却把戴森球建筑在她的周围，彻底挡住她的光芒。"
ADD utopia.31.desc:0 "$utopia.31.intro$\n\nThough it will take many years before we can tell the difference from here, the notion that she won't be watching over future generations has shaken our people and they deserve a formal apology."
CN2 utopia.31.desc:0 "$utopia.31.intro$尽管我们人民要花很多年才能彻底看不到游荡者的光芒，但是当大家得知游荡者将无法继续守望我们的下一代时，都感到痛不欲生。你欠我们一个郑重的道歉。"
ADD utopia.31.a:0 "Issue a formal apology."
CN2 utopia.31.a:0 "发表正式的道歉。"
ADD utopia.31.b:0 "Share some of our energy with them."
CN2 utopia.31.b:0 "把我们的一些能源分享给他们。"
ADD utopia.31.c:0 "But we're not sorry..."
CN2 utopia.31.c:0 "但我们并不感到抱歉……"
ADD utopia.32.name:0 "The One-Eyed Wanderer"
CN2 utopia.32.name:0 "独眼游荡者"
ADD utopia.32.desc:0 "$utopia.31.intro$\n\nThough it will take many years before we can tell the difference from here, our people are crushed that she won't be watching over future generations. You on the other hand, will soon have all the energy you require. A small donation of 1000 credits however, might help alleviate the pain you've caused."
CN2 utopia.32.desc:0 "$utopia.31.intro$尽管我们人民要花很多年才能彻底看不到游荡者的光芒，但是当大家得知游荡者将无法继续守望我们的下一代时，都感到痛不欲生。而你们却很快会收获大量的能源。不过你们要是捐献1000能源给我们的话，那应该能缓解你们给我们人民所带来的伤痛。"
ADD utopia.32.a:0 "Make a "donation" of 1000 credits."
CN2 utopia.32.a:0 "进行1000能源的“捐献”。"
ADD utopia.32.b:0 "We have no credits to spare, but issue a formal apology."
CN2 utopia.32.b:0 "我们没有多余能源可以给你们，但我们可以发表一个正式的道歉。"
ADD utopia.32.c:0 "What we do within our borders is none of their concern."
CN2 utopia.32.c:0 "我们国境内的事务他们无权过问。"
ADD utopia.33.name:0 "The Blind Wanderer"
CN2 utopia.33.name:0 "盲目游荡者"
ADD utopia.33.desc:0 "Today [dysonsphere_builder.GetRulerTitle] [dysonsphere_builder.GetRulerName] of the [dysonsphere_builder.GetName] met with [dyson_sphere_neighbor.GetRulerTitle] [dyson_sphere_neighbor.GetRulerName] in person to issue a formal apology to our empire for blinding the One-eyed Wanderer. They offered their sincerest regrets and remain confident that the Wanderer will continue to guide us, as she always has, using her strength of will and sense of justice, and not her sight."
CN2 utopia.33.desc:0 "今天， [dysonsphere_builder.GetName] 的 [dysonsphere_builder.GetRulerTitle]   [dysonsphere_builder.GetRulerName] 与 [dyson_sphere_neighbor.GetRulerTitle]   [dyson_sphere_neighbor.GetRulerName] 进行了会面，为他们挡住了独眼游荡者的光芒一事而向我们帝国正式道歉，他们向我们真诚的表示了自己的懊悔，并向我们保证，虽然游荡者失去了光芒，但她一定会用她的信念和公义之心继续引导着我们的民族。"
ADD utopia.33.a:0 "That she will."
CN2 utopia.33.a:0 "游荡者的信念将引我们前行。"
ADD utopia.33.b:0 "They're not sorry enough."
CN2 utopia.33.b:0 "他们的道歉不够真诚。"
ADD utopia.34.name:0 "The Blind Wanderer"
CN2 utopia.34.name:0 "盲目游荡者"
ADD utopia.34.desc:0 "We have received your request and could not help but notice that there appears to be some confusion regarding the nature of our relationship. Allow us to clarify. [dyson_system.GetName] is a star within our space, and though this concept may be difficult for you to grasp, what happens within our space does not concern you. As it does not concern us whether you are capable of pleasing your people or not.\n\nTo avoid further confusion, in the future you will do well to remember this."
CN2 utopia.34.desc:0 "我们已经收到了你们的请求，但我们发现你们对我们之间的关系似乎有些误解，让我们澄清一下。 [dyson_system.GetName] 是我们国境内的恒星，虽然国境的概念对你们来说可能有些难以理解，不过请搞清楚我们国境内的事务与你们无关，这就如同你们如何安抚你们的人民与我们无关一样。为了以后不再出现误会，你们最好记住这点。"
ADD utopia.34.a:0 "Don't dignify them with a response."
CN2 utopia.34.a:0 "他们根本不值得我们做出回应。"
ADD utopia.34.b:0 "Send them an insult."
CN2 utopia.34.b:0 "羞辱他们。"
ADD utopia.34.b.tooltip:0 ""Your pitiful empire will soon learn the meaning of being alone without a friend in the universe...""
CN2 utopia.34.b.tooltip:0 "“你们那可怜的帝国很快就会明白在宇宙中孤立无援是什么感觉……”"
ADD utopia.34.c:0 "One day we'll make them sorry..."
CN2 utopia.34.c:0 "总有一天我们要让他们付出代价……"
ADD utopia.35.name:0 "The Blind Wanderer"
CN2 utopia.35.name:0 "盲目游荡者"
ADD utopia.35.desc:0 "Today [dysonsphere_builder.GetRulerTitle] [dysonsphere_builder.GetRulerName] of the [dysonsphere_builder.GetName] met with [dyson_sphere_neighbor.GetRulerTitle] [dyson_sphere_neighbor.GetRulerName] in person to issue a formal apology to our empire for blinding the One-eyed Wanderer. They also offered us a gift of 1000 energy in the hopes of repairing some of the damage they've caused, and expressed confidence that the Wanderer will continue to guide us, as she always has, using her strength of will and sense of justice rather than her sight."
CN2 utopia.35.desc:0 "今天， [dysonsphere_builder.GetName] 的 [dysonsphere_builder.GetRulerTitle]   [dysonsphere_builder.GetRulerName] 与 [dyson_sphere_neighbor.GetRulerTitle]   [dyson_sphere_neighbor.GetRulerName] 进行了会面，为他们挡住了独眼游荡者的光芒一事而向我们帝国正式道歉， 他们还给我们捐献了1000能源，希望能借此弥补他们给我们人民所造成的情感伤害，他们还向我们保证，虽然游荡者失去了光芒，但她一定会用她的信念和公义之心继续引导着我们的民族。"
ADD utopia.35.a:0 "That she will."
CN2 utopia.35.a:0 "游荡者的信念将引我们前行。"
ADD utopia.35.b:0 "They're not sorry enough."
CN2 utopia.35.b:0 "他们的道歉不够真诚。"
ADD utopia.36.desc:0 "Today [dysonsphere_builder.GetRulerTitle] [dysonsphere_builder.GetRulerName] of the [dysonsphere_builder.GetName] met with [dyson_sphere_neighbor.GetRulerTitle] [dyson_sphere_neighbor.GetRulerName] in person to issue a formal apology to our empire for blinding the One-eyed Wanderer. Though the apology seemed sincere, they refused to give us due compensation, claiming that they did not have the energy to spare."
CN2 utopia.36.desc:0 "今天， [dysonsphere_builder.GetName] 的 [dysonsphere_builder.GetRulerTitle]   [dysonsphere_builder.GetRulerName] 与 [dyson_sphere_neighbor.GetRulerTitle]   [dyson_sphere_neighbor.GetRulerName] 进行了会面，为他们挡住了独眼游荡者的光芒一事而向我们帝国正式道歉，尽管他们的道歉很真诚，但他们拒绝给我们提供能源补偿，他们说没有多余能源可以分享给我们。"
ADD utopia.36.a:0 "They did their best."
CN2 utopia.36.a:0 "他们已经尽力弥补了。"
ADD utopia.36.b:0 "Cheapskates!"
CN2 utopia.36.b:0 "这帮吝啬鬼！"
ADD utopia.37.desc:0 "In an attempt to repair some of the damage done to the people of the [dyson_sphere_neighbor.GetName], when we accidentally constructed a Dyson Sphere around one of their most beloved stars, our [dysonsphere_builder.GetRulerTitle] traveled all the way to their homeworld to deliver a sincere apology. Yet, they have made it painstakingly clear that our efforts have been insufficient."
CN2 utopia.37.desc:0 "由于我们意外的在 [dyson_sphere_neighbor.GetName] 的人民最爱戴的恒星附近修建了一个戴森球，我们伤害到了他们的感情，为了做出补偿，我们的 [dysonsphere_builder.GetRulerTitle] 特地去了他们的国家，向他们的人民致以诚挚的歉意。遗憾的是，他们认为我们光道歉是不够的。"
ADD utopia.37.a:0 "What a shame."
CN2 utopia.37.a:0 "太可惜了。"
ADD utopia.37.b:0 "How ungrateful."
CN2 utopia.37.b:0 "这群蹬鼻子上脸的家伙。"
ADD utopia.38.desc:0 "In an attempt to repair some of the damage done to the relation between our empire and the [dyson_sphere_neighbor.GetName], following the construction of a Dyson Sphere around one of their most beloved stars, our [dysonsphere_builder.GetRulerTitle] traveled all the way to their homeworld to deliver a sincere apology to their people.\n\nThough it may take them some time to recover from their loss, they appreciated that we made an effort. Hopefully from now on the relations between our empires will only improve."
CN2 utopia.38.desc:0 "由于我们意外的在 [dyson_sphere_neighbor.GetName] 的人民最爱戴的恒星附近修建了一个戴森球，我们伤害到了他们的感情，为了修补两国之间的关系，我们的 [dysonsphere_builder.GetRulerTitle] 特地去了他们的国家，去向他们的人民致以诚挚的歉意。尽管他们需要时间来弥合伤痛，但他们对我们的道歉之举感到十分满意，希望我们两国之间的关系能够由此而更进一步。"
ADD utopia.38.a:0 "That's good news."
CN2 utopia.38.a:0 "真是个好消息。"
ADD utopia.39.desc:0 "We thank you for taking the time to enlighten us, as it seems we were indeed confused about many things. The true nature of your kind among others.\n\nYour pitiful empire will soon learn the meaning of being alone without a friend in the universe."
CN2 utopia.39.desc:0 "我们很感谢你们特地花时间来告知我们，看来我们之前有很多事情没搞清楚，其中之一就是你们人民的本性。你们那可怜的帝国很快就会明白在宇宙中孤立无援是什么感觉。"
ADD utopia.39.a:0 "We look forward to that day."
CN2 utopia.39.a:0 "我们期待着那一天。"
ADD utopia.39.b:0 "They'll pay for their insolence!"
CN2 utopia.39.b:0 "他们要为自己的无礼付出代价！"
ADD utopia.39.c:0 "Talk is cheap."
CN2 utopia.39.c:0 "光说不练的家伙。"
ADD utopia.40.desc:0 "Our informants report that the [dyson_sphere_neighbor.GetName] were greatly displeased by our refusal to issue a formal apology to their people for blocking the light of a central star in one of their star constellations. Though we've had no word from them regarding the incident, the [dysonsphere_builder.GetRulerTitle] expressed their disappointment in a speech addressing the empire."
CN2 utopia.40.desc:0 "我们的线人报告说 [dyson_sphere_neighbor.GetName] 对我们拒绝为挡住他们星座的中央恒星一事道歉而感到很不满。尽管他们并未针对此事和我们联系， [dysonsphere_builder.GetRulerTitle] 还是在一篇演讲中向我们国民表达了他们帝国人民的失望情绪。"
ADD utopia.40.a:0 "That's unfortunate."
CN2 utopia.40.a:0 "太可惜了。"
ADD utopia.40.b:0 "That's not our problem."
CN2 utopia.40.b:0 "与我们无关。"
ADD utopia.51.name:0 "Fountain of Youth"
CN2 utopia.51.name:0 "青春之泉"
ADD utopia.51.desc:0 "The board of the Science Nexus are thrilled to announce that they have been given a unique opportunity to recruit widely acclaimed researcher Dr. Xhaxxore, a prominent name within the field of life-extension.\n\nHe and his staff were in the final stages of developing a serum that has shown good promise of prolonging life, when they ran out of funds. Hiring Dr. Xhaxxore however, means we will not have the resources to continue our current research into organic engineering, led by Dr. Groik. She is attempting to streamline engineering research with the use of an organic supercomputer."
CN2 utopia.51.desc:0 "科学联合学院董事会兴高采烈地宣布他们有机会招募到声名远扬的研究员哈克索利博士，后者在延长自然寿命领域上颇有建树。他和他的团队正在研制可以延长寿命的血清，目前已经到了研发的最终阶段，但他们的科研经费却用完了。如果此时雇用哈克索利博士，我们将没有多余的经费来继续进行由古罗瑞克博士领导的有机生物工程领域的研究，古罗瑞克博士目前正打算使用有机生物超级电脑来将工程研究进行流水线处理。"
ADD utopia.51.a:0 "Recruit Dr. Xhaxxore for 1000 credits."
CN2 utopia.51.a:0 "用1000点数来招募哈克索利博士。"
ADD utopia.51.b:0 "Prioritize Dr. Groik's research."
CN2 utopia.51.b:0 "优先完成古罗瑞克博士的研究。"
ADD utopia.51.c:0 "We can't afford to hire Dr. Xhaxxore."
CN2 utopia.51.c:0 "我们目前还雇不起哈克索利博士。"
ADD utopia.54.name:0 "Suspicious Minds"
CN2 utopia.54.name:0 "心生疑窦"
ADD utopia.54.desc:0 "Dr. Xhaxxore and his team demonstrated the results from their research earlier this week. The serum, when applied to the skin, causes unprecedented cell regeneration, supposedly thanks to the miracle ingredient, "essence of [missing_pops_planet.GetName]", named after its mysterious origin.\n\nSadly, there have been complaints from a few individuals regarding the additional funding Xhaxxore received. Dr. Groik has even gone so far as to accuse Xhaxxore of being a fraud. Now she requests permission, as well as an additional budget of 500 credits, to launch a secret investigation. If Xhaxxore finds out he might take offense and leave."
CN2 utopia.54.desc:0 "哈克索利博士和他的团队在这周展现了他们的研究成果，他们研制的血清如果用在皮肤上，会让皮肤进行史无前例的细胞再生，这都要归功于由 [ointment_name.GetName] 所提取的神奇原料。但遗憾的是，有几个工作人员针对哈克索利博士接受了额外的研究经费一事进行投诉，古罗瑞克博士甚至怒批哈克索利是个骗子。古罗瑞克博士希望能对哈克索利进行秘密调查，并同时希望得到500点数做为调查的资金。如果哈克索利发现古罗瑞克在调查他，那么他可能会愤而离去。"
ADD utopia.54.a:0 "There's nothing to back her claims."
CN2 utopia.54.a:0 "古罗瑞克博士的指控毫无根据。"
ADD utopia.54.b:0 "Investigate, to be on the safe side."
CN2 utopia.54.b:0 "为了安全起见，还是调查一下吧。"
ADD utopia.54.c:0 "Our budget won't allow it."
CN2 utopia.54.c:0 "我们可没有多余预算去搞什么秘密调查。"
ADD utopia.55.name:0 "Essence of [ointment_name.GetName]"
CN2 utopia.55.name:0 " [ointment_name.GetName] 的精华"
ADD utopia.55.desc:0 "Dr. Groik's investigation into Xhaxxore's research has yielded some interesting results. Not only has Dr. Xhaxxore greatly exaggerated the effects of the serum, he has neglected to mention that they are only temporary. The side-effects, however, when over-used, can be quite permanent.\n\nThe essence itself has been extracted from a gland found in a species native to the [ointment_name.GetName] system, none other than the [target_country.GetSpeciesName] of the [target_country.GetName]. Xhaxxore has held several [target_country.GetSpeciesNamePlural] in cryostasis for months to secure the necessary supply of essence. It is likely that our diplomatic ties with their empire would suffer if they were to discover the truth."
CN2 utopia.55.desc:0 "古罗瑞克博士对哈克索利进行了调查，发现了一些很有意思的事情，原来哈克索利博士不但夸大了他血清的实际效果，还隐瞒了其血清只有短期效果这一事实，还有，如果过度使用血清的话，会产生不可逆转的永久性副作用。制作血清所需的神奇原料是从 [ointment_name.GetName] 星系中的某种生物的腺体上所提取，而这种生物恰恰是 [target_country.GetName] 的 [target_country.GetSpeciesName] 。哈克索利将几只 [target_country.GetSpeciesAdj] 进行冷冻休眠，从而确保血清所需的必要原料的供给。如果此事被发现的话，我国与那个生物所在的国家之间的外交关系将会恶化。"
ADD utopia.55.a:0 "Terminate the project and apprehend Xhaxxore. No one can know."
CN2 utopia.55.a:0 "终止研究并逮捕哈克索利，此事不能让其他人知道。"
ADD utopia.55.b:0 "Silence Groik and market the product as anti-aging cream."
CN2 utopia.55.b:0 "命令古罗瑞克不准声张此事，并把研究产品命名为抗衰老面霜。"
ADD utopia.55.b.tooltip:0 "With an intense marketing campaign the product may yield a hefty profit in the near future."
CN2 utopia.55.b.tooltip:0 "只要进行足够的市场宣传，这项产品可以在短时间内获得巨大的经济收益。"
ADD utopia.56.name:0 "Fountain of Youth"
CN2 utopia.56.name:0 "青春之泉"
ADD utopia.56.desc:0 "Regrettably the mysterious Dr. Xhaxxore has slipped through our clutches, leaving his staff and test-subjects behind. The [target_country.GetSpeciesNamePlural] have been awoken and thankfully have no recollection of what they've been through. As for Xhaxxore he is probably already on his way to some distant system, under a different name, plotting his next con. With a little luck, the next time he slips up we will be there to catch him.\n\nHis disgraced staff seem to have been as blindsided as we were by his charm, and many have offered to join the Science Nexus permanently to make up for their mistakes."
CN2 utopia.56.desc:0 "很遗憾，那个神秘的哈克索利博士从我们手中溜走了，他的团队和测试样本全被他抛弃了。 [target_country.GetSpeciesNamePlural] 已经被唤醒，他们完全不记得自己所遭遇的一切。至于哈克索利，他很可能已经溜到某个偏远的星系并改头换面打算继续行骗。希望下次我们能在他开溜前抓到他。哈克索利手下的研究团队成员也和我们一样被他所骗，为了弥补他们所犯下的错误，很多人希望加入科学联合学院。"
ADD utopia.56.a:0 "They can't be trusted."
CN2 utopia.56.a:0 "不能信任他们。"
ADD utopia.56.b:0 "They are welcome to join us."
CN2 utopia.56.b:0 "欢迎他们加入我们。"
ADD utopia.56.c:0 "They're clearly not the brightest stars in the galaxy..."
CN2 utopia.56.c:0 "他们显然不是银河系中最聪明的研究员……"
ADD utopia.57.name:0 "Fountain of Gold"
CN2 utopia.57.name:0 "财富之泉"
ADD utopia.57.desc:0 "Marketed under the name "Ageless," the Essence of [ointment_name.GetName] has taken the galaxy by storm. Thanks to its charismatic inventor and a solid marketing campaign, the new "organic" miracle cream is being promoted everywhere. Stars, of the flesh and blood kind, in every system are "aging less with Ageless."\n\nHow the doctor has managed to procure enough [target_country.GetSpeciesAdj] glands to mass-produce the serum, however, remains a mystery..."
CN2 utopia.57.desc:0 "以“青春永驻”的名头进入市场后， [ointment_name.GetName] 精华迅速席卷了整个银河系。多亏了它那极富魅力的发明者和有力的市场宣传，现在这一最新的“有机生物”奇迹霜已经出现在银河系的各个角落，每个星系的名人们都在使用“青春永驻”来延缓衰老。至于如何获取足量的 [target_country.GetSpeciesAdj] 腺体来大规模制造这一血清，这就不为人知了……"
ADD utopia.57.a:0 "Ignorance is bliss."
CN2 utopia.57.a:0 "无知是一种幸福。"
ADD utopia.100.name:0 "Unusual disappearances on [missing_pops_planet.GetName]"
CN2 utopia.100.name:0 " [missing_pops_planet.GetName] 发生异常失踪"
ADD utopia.100.desc:0 "Unrest is rising on [missing_pops_planet.GetName] in light of a recent wave of planetwide disappearances. Several thousand denizens have been reported missing in the last two months alone and the vast majority are from marginalized and isolated groups in remote areas. This could explain why it has taken so long to come to our attention.\n\nLocal law enforcement has requested additional resources to handle the growing unrest while they continue their investigation."
CN2 utopia.100.desc:0 "在 [missing_pops_planet.GetName] 各地最近发生了失踪事件之后，开始变得动荡不安。仅仅在上两个月就有数千人失踪，而且大多数都来自偏远地区的边缘或孤立社会。这或许可以解释为何过了这么久才引起我们的注意。\n\n当地的秩序维持机构已请求更多资源，以在继续调查时应付日益增长的动乱情势。"
ADD utopia.100.a:0 "Deploy a task force to [missing_pops_planet.GetName]."
CN2 utopia.100.a:0 "部署一支特遣队到 [missing_pops_planet.GetName] 。"
ADD utopia.100.b:0 "Surely they were marginalized for a reason..."
CN2 utopia.100.b:0 "他们边缘化肯定是有理由的……"
ADD utopia.101.name:0 "Castles in the Sky"
CN2 utopia.101.name:0 "天空之城"
ADD utopia.101.desc:0 "The investigation into the missing denizens of [missing_pops_planet.GetName] has revealed that they were all offered a job at a soon-to-open space casino called "Sky Castle," by sharp dressed recruiters speaking an unidentified alien language. Further inquiry has revealed that if such a casino does in fact exist, it is not within any known part of the galaxy.\n\nAs the presence of the strike force seems to be deterring the kidnappers from striking again they have been relieved to give local law enforcement a chance of luring the abductors back out."
CN2 utopia.101.desc:0 "对 [missing_pops_planet.GetName] 失踪者的调查表明，他们都被一位打扮潇洒，且说着不明外星语言的招募者雇佣，前往一家即将开张的太空娱乐城“天空之城”任职。进一步调查显示，如果这座娱乐城真的存在，那也不位于银河系中任何已知的部分。\n\n鉴于突击队的存在似乎使绑架者不敢再次出手，他们现已被召回，以便当地秩序维持机构有机会引蛇出洞。"
ADD utopia.101.a:0 "Disconcerting."
CN2 utopia.101.a:0 "令人不安。"
ADD utopia.102.name:0 "Age less with Ageless"
CN2 utopia.102.name:0 "延缓衰老不老霜"
ADD utopia.102.desc:0 "Some of our scientists have raised the alarm on a new "all organic" anti-aging cream called Ageless, that is being sold throughout the empire by a seemingly questionable distributor.\n\nAdvertised under the slogan "Age less with Ageless", the wildly popular cosmeceutical is said to promote cell regeneration with a "unique formula" containing the mysterious miracle ingredient "Essence of [ointment_name.GetName]".\n\nThough it can cause some very disturbing side-effects the product has shown real potential of stimulating cell growth and our research council highly recommends procuring a shipment to recreate its formula."
CN2 utopia.102.desc:0 "我们有些科学家发出了警告，要我们警惕一种名为不老霜的“全有机”抗衰老霜，目前正在由一家似乎很可疑的经销商在我们的帝国内销售。\n\n打着“延缓衰老不老霜”的宣传口号，这种人气爆棚的药用化妆品据称有着“独特配方”，含有一种神秘的神奇原料“ [ointment_name.GetName] 之精华”，可以促进细胞再生。\n\n尽管它会造成一些非常令人不安的副作用，该产品确实可以促进细胞生长，并且我们的科研协会强烈推荐我们购买一批产品来重现其配方。"
ADD utopia.102.a:0 "Improved cell regeneration sounds promising."
CN2 utopia.102.a:0 "改善细胞再生听起来很不错。"
ADD utopia.102.b:0 "Wrinkle reduction is hardly a national concern."
CN2 utopia.102.b:0 "祛皱算不上是帝国问题。"
ADD utopia.103.name:0 "Essence of...[target_country.GetSpeciesName]"
CN2 utopia.103.name:0 " [target_country.GetSpeciesName] ……之精华"
ADD utopia.103.desc:0 "A thorough analysis of the anti-aging cream "Ageless" has revealed that the origin of the rejuvenating miracle ingredient, "Essence of [ointment_name.GetName]", is quite close to home. In fact it can only be extracted from the glands of live [target_country.GetSpeciesNamePlural], in a barbaric procedure that is undoubtedly both painful and dangerous.\n\nIn better news these finds have allowed us to create an injection that stimulates the gland, improving life-expectancy significantly. It seems that the key to regeneration was inside us all along!"
CN2 utopia.103.desc:0 "对抗衰老霜“不老霜”的全面分析揭露了其神奇再生原料，“ [ointment_name.GetName] 之精华”的来源深深地令人感到不安。事实上它只能从活生生的 [target_country.GetSpeciesNamePlural] 腺体中提取，而野蛮的提取手段无疑也非常痛苦并且危险。\n\n好消息是，这些发现使我们可以创造一种注射液来刺激这些腺体，并极大地增加寿命。看来再生的关键一直都在我们体内！"
ADD utopia.103.a:0 "Find the vile creatures that did this to us!"
CN2 utopia.103.a:0 "找到那个对我们做出这种事的邪恶生物！"
ADD utopia.103.b:0 "Forgive and forget..."
CN2 utopia.103.b:0 "既往不咎……"
ADD utopia.104.name:0 "Gland Thieves"
CN2 utopia.104.name:0 "腺体盗贼"
ADD utopia.104.desc:0 "In a coordinated effort between the military and the society research department, we have followed the distribution chain of the "Ageless" anti-aging cream back to a Science Nexus owned by the [fountain_of_youth_country.GetName], where it was developed by a government-employed researcher named Dr. Xhaxxore and his team.\n\nThe [fountain_of_youth_country.GetName] has been making a huge profit off of the product and it seems unlikely that they wouldn't know the source of its key ingredient."
CN2 utopia.104.desc:0 "在军团与社会科研部门的合作下，我们沿着抗衰老霜“不老霜”的销售过程顺藤摸瓜，找到了一家 [fountain_of_youth_country.GetName] 拥有的科学联合学院，一位名叫艾克萨索的博士和他的团队受雇于帝国，在那里开发了这种产品。\n\n [fountain_of_youth_country.GetName] 靠这产品赚了一大笔利润，并且不太可能不知道其关键原料的来源。"
ADD utopia.104.a:0 "They must release the victims and withdraw the product immediately."
CN2 utopia.104.a:0 "他们必须立即释放受害者，并将产品下架。"
ADD utopia.104.a.tooltip:0 "Sends an envoy with our civilly worded request."
CN2 utopia.104.a.tooltip:0 "派一位使者去好言相劝。"
ADD utopia.104.c:0 "Actions speak louder than words."
CN2 utopia.104.c:0 "行动胜于空谈。"
ADD utopia.104.c.tooltip:0 "It is much too late for diplomatic exchanges."
CN2 utopia.104.c.tooltip:0 "外交往来已经太晚了。"
ADD utopia.104.d:0 "We cannot risk a diplomatic incident."
CN2 utopia.104.d:0 "我们不能冒引发外交事件的风险。"
ADD utopia.105.name:0 "Ageless Scheme Exposed"
CN2 utopia.105.name:0 "不老霜计划败露"
ADD utopia.105.desc:0 "We have had word from the [target_country.GetSpeciesNamePlural] who claim to have uncovered evidence of our involvement in the kidnapping and unlawful imprisonment of several of their kind, for the purpose of extracting a cell regenerating enzyme from their glands.\n\nThey demand that we release them and withdraw the product in the interest of keeping the peace between our empires. Adhering to their demands would mean the premature end to our clandestine credit-generating scheme..."
CN2 utopia.105.desc:0 " [target_country.GetSpeciesNamePlural] 给我们发来了消息，声称他们发现了证据，证明我们牵涉不法绑架数名他们的人民，以从他们的腺体中提取一种细胞再生酶。\n\n他们要求我们释放他们，并将产品下架以维持双方帝国之间的和平。听从他们的要求意味着我们的秘密赚钱计划要提前结束了……"
ADD utopia.105.a:0 "Agree to their demands."
CN2 utopia.105.a:0 "同意他们的要求。"
ADD utopia.105.b:0 "Deny everything!"
CN2 utopia.105.b:0 "否认一切！"
ADD utopia.105.c:0 "We have no interest in keeping the peace..."
CN2 utopia.105.c:0 "我们无意维持和平……"
ADD utopia.105.c.tooltip:0 "Ignores their request."
CN2 utopia.105.c.tooltip:0 "无视他们的要求。"
ADD utopia.106.name:0 "The Essence of Justice"
CN2 utopia.106.name:0 "正义的本质"
ADD utopia.106.desc:0 "We have fought the good fight and won!\n\nThough the [fountain_of_youth_country.GetName] claim they never knew of the sinister origins of the "Essence of [ointment_name.GetName]," which is clearly a lie, at least they had the decency of returning our citizens to their home on [missing_pops_planet.GetName].\n\nAs for Dr. Xhaxxore, the head researcher and mastermind behind the scheme, he has escaped under mysterious circumstances, but the rest of his team is being brought to justice."
CN2 utopia.106.desc:0 "我们打了正义之仗并胜利了！\n\n尽管 [fountain_of_youth_country.GetName] 声称自己对“ [ointment_name.GetName] 之精华”的邪恶来源毫不知情，这明显是谎言，但至少他们把我们的人放回了 [missing_pops_planet.GetName] 。\n\n至于首席研究员与整个计划的策划者艾克萨索博士，他已经神秘地逃脱了，但他其余的团伙成员都已遭到了正义的制裁。"
ADD utopia.106.a:0 "It's better than nothing."
CN2 utopia.106.a:0 "总比没有好。"
ADD utopia.107.name:0 "Scum of the Universe"
CN2 utopia.107.name:0 "宇宙的渣滓"
ADD utopia.107.desc.a:0 "We have received a formal reply from the [fountain_of_youth_country.GetName], forcefully denying their involvement in the production of the "Ageless" anti-aging cream and encouraging us to find "a more constructive outlet for our apparent inferiority complex towards the superior [fountain_of_youth_country.GetSpeciesNamePlural], than the fabrication of toothless accusations"."
CN2 utopia.107.desc.a:0 "我们收到了 [fountain_of_youth_country.GetName] 的正式回复，强硬地否认了他们与抗衰老霜“不老霜”的生产有关，并鼓励我们“为面对更优秀的 [fountain_of_youth_country.GetSpeciesNamePlural] 的自卑情结寻找一种更有建设性的发泄方法，而不是捏造毫无根据的指控”。"
ADD utopia.107.a:0 "Scum of the Universe!"
CN2 utopia.107.a:0 "宇宙的渣滓！"
ADD utopia.107.desc.b:0 "We have had no response from the [target_country.GetName] regarding their involvement in the kidnapping of our kind for the purpose of producing the anti-aging cream "Ageless". But word has it Dr. Xhaxxore has fled with most of what was left of the essence, finally putting an end to their profiteering.\n\nOur thoughts go out today to the doctor's many victims who are still in captivity, and their families back on [missing_pops_planet.GetName]."
CN2 utopia.107.desc.b:0 "关于 [target_country.GetName] 牵涉绑架我们的人民用于制造抗衰老霜“不老霜”一事，我们没有收到任何回应。但有消息称艾克萨索博士已经带着剩余的精华逃跑了，给他们的牟利画上了句号。\n\n我们对那些仍被博士关押着的受害者们，以及他们在 [missing_pops_planet.GetName] 上的家人表示同情。"
ADD utopia.108.name:0 "Dr. Xhaxxore has fled!"
CN2 utopia.108.name:0 "艾克萨索博士逃跑了！"
ADD utopia.108.desc:0 "The [target_country.GetSpeciesNamePlural] were not pleased that we denied our involvement in the kidnapping of their kind. What's more Dr. Xhaxxore, smelling smoke, has fled taking his supply of essence with him, making it impossible to produce more Ageless cream."
CN2 utopia.108.desc:0 " [target_country.GetSpeciesNamePlural] 对我们否认牵涉绑架一事表示不满。而且艾克萨索博士看到苗头不对，已经带着精华逃跑了，使我们无法继续生产抗衰老霜。"
ADD utopia.108.a:0 "Drat it..."
CN2 utopia.108.a:0 "可恶……"
ADD utopia.58.name:0 "The Essence of Nothing"
CN2 utopia.58.name:0 "一无是处的精华"
ADD utopia.58.desc:0 "Xhaxxore is gone and he's taken all his research with him, leaving only his bewildered staff behind. They were as blindsided by his sudden disappearance as we were, and though all attest to the content of his character, painting a portrait of a charismatic and charitable genius who would do anything for his team, they could only offer anecdotal evidence of his achievements.\n\nWe can only speculate as to whether Dr. Groik was right to call him a fraud, or whether he took his miracle essence to a higher bidder. If he ever tries a similar scheme elsewhere, we will find him."
CN2 utopia.58.desc:0 "哈克索利消失了，他把他的所有研究成果也一并带走了，只留下了他手下那群一头雾水的团队成员。哈克索利的团队也和我们一样被哈克索利给骗了，尽管他们都认为哈克索利是个人品魅力俱佳的天才，是个为了团队不惜奉献一切的无私统治者，但是他们却拿不出什么证据以证明哈克索利的真正成就。古罗瑞克博士对哈克索利是骗子的指控到底是否属实，不得而知。我们也不知道哈克索利是不是把他的研究成果卖给了出价更高的国家。当然了，如果他再在其他星系玩类似把戏的话，我们一定会抓到他的。"
ADD utopia.58.a:0 "Scoundrel!"
CN2 utopia.58.a:0 "这个混蛋！"
ADD utopia.59.intro:0 "Dr. Groik and her team have invented a neural bank - an organic computer that stores and harnesses the collective cognitive power of all brains that are uploaded to its drive, greatly improving our research speed. But there's one hitch - to function properly, the uploaded brains have to be extracted from the subjects' bodies and placed within a tank of conductive fluids. Since our bodies can not survive long without a brain, subjects will have to leave their material existence behind."
CN2 utopia.59.intro:0 "古罗瑞克博士和她的团队发明了一个神经网络库——一个可以将上传到其存储设备中的所有大脑的集合意识善加利用的有机生物电脑，它可以大幅加快我们的研究进度。但有一个缺点，那就是为了能够运转正常，所有被上传到神经网络银行的大脑必须从身体中剥离出来并放置在导电的溶液罐中。由于我们的身体没了大脑就无法存活，因此想加入神经网络库的人必须彻底抛弃他们自己的肉体。"
ADD utopia.59.name:0 "Neural Bank"
CN2 utopia.59.name:0 "神经网络库"
ADD utopia.59.desc:0 "$utopia.59.intro$\n\nAs expected, volunteers have not been lining up. So far there has been only one - science leader [volunteer_leader.GetName]."
CN2 utopia.59.desc:0 "$utopia.59.intro$和我们预料的一样，想进入神经网络库的志愿者寥寥无几。目前只有一个志愿者——那就是科学统治者 [volunteer_leader.GetName] 。"
ADD utopia.59.a:0 "Upload [volunteer_leader.GetName]'s brain to the Nexus."
CN2 utopia.59.a:0 "将 [volunteer_leader.GetName] 的大脑上传到科学联合学院。"
ADD utopia.59.a.tooltip:1 "The Science Nexus will now produce an additional:\n£physics£ §G50§! £society£ §G50§! £engineering£ §G50§!"
CN2 utopia.59.a.tooltip:1 "科学枢纽现在将额外产出：\n£physics£ §G50§! £society£ §G50§! £engineering£ §G50§!"
ADD utopia.59.b:0 "That would be unethical."
CN2 utopia.59.b:0 "此举太不道德。"
ADD utopia.59.c:0 "No, [volunteer_leader.GetName] is needed elsewhere."
CN2 utopia.59.c:0 "不行， [volunteer_leader.GetName] 还有其他必须履行的职责。"
ADD utopia.60.name:0 "Neural Bank"
CN2 utopia.60.name:0 "神经网络库"
ADD utopia.60.desc:0 "$utopia.59.intro$\n\nAs expected, volunteers have not been lining up. So far there has been only one - a bright young researcher on Groik's team. However, she has a family to provide for and requests monetary compensation of 1000 credits for them."
CN2 utopia.60.desc:0 "$utopia.59.intro$和我们预料的一样，想进入神经网络库的志愿者寥寥无几。目前只有一个志愿者——那就是古罗瑞克团队中的一名杰出的年轻研究员。但她是有家室的人，她要求为她的家人提供1000能源的补偿。"
ADD utopia.60.a:0 "Unfortunately we can't afford it."
CN2 utopia.60.a:0 "不巧的是我们没有足够的预算可以支付给她的家人。"
ADD utopia.60.b:0 "That sounds reasonable."
CN2 utopia.60.b:0 "这个要求合情合理。"
ADD utopia.60.c:0 "That would be unethical."
CN2 utopia.60.c:0 "此举太不道德。"
ADD utopia.62.name:0 "[abducted_leader.GetName]"
CN2 utopia.62.name:0 " [abducted_leader.GetName] "
ADD utopia.62.desc:0 "Just now the staff of the Science Nexus physics department simultaneously blacked out for almost 15 minutes. When they woke up again physics leader [abducted_leader.GetName], was missing, [abducted_leader.GetHerHis] office had been upturned, [abducted_leader.GetHerHis] storage emptied and [abducted_leader.GetHerHis] drives fried.\n\n[abducted_leader.GetHerHisCap] colleagues believe that's where [abducted_leader.GetSheHe] kept data on a personal project [abducted_leader.GetSheHe] was working on. Though tight-lipped about [abducted_leader.GetHerHis] research, it seems [abducted_leader.GetSheHe] was nearing a breakthrough.\n\nSeveral of the staff mentioned seeing a bright purple light before losing consciousness. There have been no other clues as to [abducted_leader.GetHerHis] whereabouts."
CN2 utopia.62.desc:0 "刚才，科学联合学院物理部门的全部研究人员都昏迷了15分钟。当他们醒来时，发现物理部门的首席研究员 [abducted_leader.GetName] 失踪了， [abducted_leader.GetHerHis] 的办公室被翻了个底朝天， [abducted_leader.GetHerHis] 的存储室被清空了，而 [abducted_leader.GetHerHis] 的存储设备也被毁掉。 [abducted_leader.GetHerHisCap] 的同事认为那是 [abducted_leader.GetSheHe] 存储 [abducted_leader.GetSheHe] 的个人科研项目的数据资料的地方。虽然 [abducted_leader.GetHerHis] 对其个人科研项目闭口不谈，但大家都认为 [abducted_leader.GetSheHe] 的研究很快就要获得重大突破。有几名研究人员说他们在失去意识前曾看到一束明亮的紫光，除此之外就没有其他有用信息了，我们无从得知 [abducted_leader.GetHerHis] 目前所在的位置。"
ADD utopia.62.a:0 "Continue the search."
CN2 utopia.62.a:0 "继续搜索"
ADD utopia.63.name:0 "[abducted_leader.GetName]"
CN2 utopia.63.name:0 " [abducted_leader.GetName] "
ADD utopia.63.desc:0 "Early this morning the Science Nexus staff discovered missing physics leader [abducted_leader.GetName] in the canteen, having breakfast, as if nothing happened.\n\n[abducted_leader.GetSheHeCap] claims [abducted_leader.GetSheHe] awoke in [abducted_leader.GetHerHis] bed just moments previously and has no recollection of ever leaving the Science Nexus. But several of [abducted_leader.GetHerHis] colleagues have voiced concerns that [abducted_leader.GetSheHe]'s making the staff uncomfortable and that [abducted_leader.GetSheHe]'s only pretending not to remember.\n\n[abducted_leader.GetSheHeCap]'s also returned with an uncanny understanding of subjects previously unknown to [abducted_leader.GetHerHim]. [abducted_leader.GetSheHe] is currently awaiting assignment."
CN2 utopia.63.desc:0 "今早，科学联合学院的研究员在餐厅发现了失踪的物理部门首席研究员 [abducted_leader.GetName] ，当时他正在吃早餐，就好像什么事都没发生过似的。 [abducted_leader.GetSheHeCap] 说 [abducted_leader.GetSheHe] 是在 [abducted_leader.GetHerHis] 的床上刚睡醒，并且不记得自己曾经离开过科学联合学院。但有几名 [abducted_leader.GetHerHis] 的同事感到很忧虑，说 [abducted_leader.GetSheHe] 让周围的人感到很不舒服，他们认为 [abducted_leader.GetSheHe] 是在假装失忆。 [abducted_leader.GetSheHeCap] 返回后，对之前 [abducted_leader.GetHerHim] 所不了解的研究领域似乎有了非常深入的了解， [abducted_leader.GetSheHe] 目前正在等候任务分配。"
ADD utopia.63.a:0 "[abducted_leader.GetSheHeCap] could be an asset."
CN2 utopia.63.a:0 " [abducted_leader.GetSheHeCap] 可以成为我们重要的助力。"
ADD utopia.63.b:0 "[abducted_leader.GetSheHeCap] could put the others at risk."
CN2 utopia.63.b:0 " [abducted_leader.GetSheHeCap] 可能会给其他人带来危险。"
ADD utopia.64.desc:0 "$utopia.59.intro$\n\nAs expected, volunteers have not been lining up. So far there has been only one - science leader [volunteer_leader.GetName]."
CN2 utopia.64.desc:0 "$utopia.59.intro$和我们预料的一样，想进入神经网络库的志愿者寥寥无几。目前只有一个志愿者——那就是科学统治者 [volunteer_leader.GetName] 。"
ADD utopia.80.name:0 "Science Nexus Construction"
CN2 utopia.80.name:0 "科学联合学院的建设"
ADD utopia.80.desc:0 "We have now begun the massive undertaking of constructing a Science Nexus. The foundation is in place and preparations are underway to add the main hub. The promise of new groundbreaking technologies and the realization of ideas beyond our wildest imaginations await. And though the road ahead is long and full of challenges, we have taken the first step.\n\nCould the endless mysteries of the universe finally be within our grasp?"
CN2 utopia.80.desc:0 "我们现在正在开始科学联合学院的大型建设工作，目前地基已经打好，接下来就要准备添加主要场馆了。崭新的划时代的科技以及我们前所未见的发明创造正在前面等着我们，尽管前方的道路布满荆棘，但我们已经迈出了坚实的第一步。宇宙那无尽的神秘终于可以尽在我们掌握之中了吗？"
ADD utopia.80.a:0 "The future is ours."
CN2 utopia.80.a:0 "未来是属于我们的。"
ADD utopia.82.name:0 "Alien Megastructure"
CN2 utopia.82.name:0 "外星巨构建筑"
ADD utopia.82.desc.a:2 "The [From.GetName] have taken on the challenge of building a Science Nexus - a research institute, so technically advanced, that it could revolutionize the scientific process completely.\n\nThe [think_tank_system.GetName] system is bustling with activity as engineers are assembling the initial build site. Regardless of whether they fail or succeed, trying alone has earned them a place among the great forerunners of our time."
CN2 utopia.82.desc.a:2 " [From.GetName] 已经接受了建造科学联合学院的挑战，这座研究院先进到可以彻底革新科学进程。\n\n在 [think_tank_system.GetName] 星系，工程师们正忙着组装初期建筑工地。无论成功与否，这次尝试都足以使他们跻身伟大时代先驱者的行列。"
ADD utopia.82.desc.b:0 "The [From.GetName] have begun to construct yet another Science Nexus, this time in the [think_tank_system.GetName] system."
CN2 utopia.82.desc.b:0 " [From.GetName] 又开始着手建造另一家科学联合学院，这一次是在 [think_tank_system.GetName] 星系中。"
ADD utopia.82.a:0 "A testament to the ingenuity of intelligent life."
CN2 utopia.82.a:0 "这正是智慧生物的天才之处。"
ADD utopia.82.b:0 "As always, they're overreaching."
CN2 utopia.82.b:0 "他们一如既往地把手伸得太远了。"
ADD utopia.82.c:0 "Crash and burn [From.GetSpeciesNamePlural]..."
CN2 utopia.82.c:0 "彻底摧毁 [From.GetSpeciesNamePlural] ……"
ADD utopia.83.name:0 "Science Nexus Hub"
CN2 utopia.83.name:0 "科学联合学院中央场馆建设完毕"
ADD utopia.83.desc:0 "The Science Nexus central hub is now in place, equipped with a state of the art singularity reactor. Our engineers are preparing to add the next, most challenging segment of the facility - the four research wings. They will be fitted with pioneering technology - able to withstand everything from violent heat to intense pressure waves and alien pathogens. They will also provide housing for our many researchers."
CN2 utopia.83.desc:0 "科学联合学院的中央场馆已经建设完毕，并配备了最黑科技的奇点反应堆。我们的工程师正准备进行下一项建设工作，也就是整个设施中最富有挑战性的四座研究室的建设。它们将配备最先进的科技，能够抵抗高温和强压以及外星病原体。这些研究室也将成为我们众多研究员的住所。"
ADD utopia.83.a:0 "We've come a long way."
CN2 utopia.83.a:0 "我们付出了巨大的努力和无数时间，终于走到这一步了。"
ADD utopia.85.name:0 "Science Nexus Research Wings"
CN2 utopia.85.name:0 "科学联合学院研究室"
ADD utopia.85.desc:0 "The first module of the four research wings is now in place and researchers and staff are already moving into the living quarters. The next and final step of construction will extend the wings, adding four sections of laboratories equipped to support our most dangerous research. Extensive security measures are being taken to ensure the staff's safety."
CN2 utopia.85.desc:0 "四个研究室的第一个单元已经就位了，研究员和工作人员已经搬进了他们的寝室，下一步建设将对这些研究室进行延伸，添加四个实验室区域来专门进行最危险的研究。为了确保员工的安全，我们进行非常严谨的安保措施。"
ADD utopia.85.a:0 "We're almost there..."
CN2 utopia.85.a:0 "很快就要完成了……"
ADD utopia.84.name:0 "Science Nexus Completed"
CN2 utopia.84.name:0 "科学联合学院建设完成"
ADD utopia.84.desc.a:0 "Today we celebrate the grand opening of the Science Nexus. With its state of the art research facilities and innovative technology we will have no trouble attracting the greatest minds from across the empire, or even the universe, should we so desire. This feat truly marks the beginning of a new era of enlightenment.\n\nIt is a big day in the history of our kind."
CN2 utopia.84.desc.a:0 "今天，我们庆祝科学联合学院正式完工，有了它那无以伦比的研究设施和极富创意的黑科技，我们就能让全帝国、甚至是全宇宙最杰出的头脑都聚集在科学联合学院。这一天将标志着科学文明启蒙新时代的开始。今天是个伟大的日子，足以载入我们种族的史册。"
ADD utopia.84.desc.b:0 "Today we celebrate the completion of yet another Science Nexus. If our previous accomplishments hadn't already, this will surely earn us a place on the forefront of scientific progress in the universe. Our technological advancements will allow us to shape the future to our liking."
CN2 utopia.84.desc.b:0 "今天我们庆祝又一所科学联合学院的建设完工，这第二所科学联合学院的建立将毫无争议的让我们获得宇宙科学先驱者的称号。我们的尖端科学技术将让我们可以更好的书写自己的未来。"
ADD utopia.84.a:0 "Indeed."
CN2 utopia.84.a:0 "确实如此。"
ADD utopia.86.name:0 "Alien Megastructure Completed"
CN2 utopia.86.name:0 "外星巨构建筑已完工"
ADD utopia.86.desc:0 "The [From.GetName] have constructed a Science Nexus, disproving all who doubted and placing them on the forefront for scientific progress. We may want to keep an eye on them, as the completion of such a structure will surely propel their technology into the future, giving them an advantage over other civilizations."
CN2 utopia.86.desc:0 " [From.GetName] 建立了科学联合学院，他们将自己视为宇宙科技的前沿开拓者，对所有质疑者统统不屑一顾。我们得对他们多加防范。在科学联合学院的帮助下，他们未来的科技势必突飞猛进，这将让他们获得比其他文明种族更大的优势。"
ADD utopia.86.a:0 "We will not be left behind."
CN2 utopia.86.a:0 "我们绝不能被他们抛在后面。"
ADD utopia.2000.name:0 "Ring World Construction"
CN2 utopia.2000.name:0 "星环世界建造"
ADD utopia.2000.desc:0 "We are now ready to begin the colossal task of building the initial frame of our future Ring World around the primary star of the [From.From.GetName] system.\n\nThe amount of resources and materials required to build this skeletal frame will be immense, and hundreds of thousands of our finest engineers stand ready to begin the process of dismantling the system's planetary bodies into matter which can be used in its construction."
CN2 utopia.2000.desc:0 "我们现在已准备好开始围绕 [From.From.GetName] 星系的主星建造我们未来的星环世界的初始框架这一艰巨的任务。我们将需要海量的资源与材料来建造这骨架，以及无数位最优秀的工程师们来准备将星系中的行星拆解为可用于星环建设的物质原料。"
ADD utopia.2000.a:0 "We are making history."
CN2 utopia.2000.a:0 "我们正在创造历史。"
ADD utopia.2002.name:0 "Ring World Project"
CN2 utopia.2002.name:0 "星环世界工程"
ADD utopia.2002.desc.a:0 "Word has reached us that the [From.GetName] has undertaken a construction project of monumental proportions in the [ringworld_system.GetName] system. They intend to build a massive Ring World around the system's primary, and as a first step they have started to convert the matter of all nearby planetary bodies into an initial metal skeleton for the megastructure."
CN2 utopia.2002.desc.a:0 "我们得到消息称 [From.GetName] 已经开始在 [ringworld_system.GetName] 星系进行超大规模的建设工程。他们试图围绕星系的主星建造一个巨大的星环世界，而且已开始着手将附近的所有行星的物质转换为该巨构建筑最初的金属骨架。"
ADD utopia.2002.desc.b:0 "We have received intelligence that the [From.GetName] is about to start construction on yet another Ring World, this time in the [ringworld_system.GetName] system! As before, their engineers are currently in the process of dismantling all planetary bodies in the system so that their resources and materials can be used in the Ring World's construction."
CN2 utopia.2002.desc.b:0 "我们得到情报称 [From.GetName] 即将开始建造另一个星环世界，这次是在 [ringworld_system.GetName] 星系！和上次一样，他们的工程师们正在拆解所有行星并将其转变为可用于星环世界建造的资源与材料。"
ADD utopia.2002.a:0 "Will it be as impressive as our own?"
CN2 utopia.2002.a:0 "它会和我们的一样伟大吗？"
ADD utopia.2002.b:0 "An impressive project... if it is ever finished."
CN2 utopia.2002.b:0 "一项了不起的工程……如果能完成的话。"
ADD utopia.2003.name:0 "Ring World Frame Completed"
CN2 utopia.2003.name:0 "星环世界骨架完成"
ADD utopia.2003.desc:0 "The skeletal frame of the Ring World we are building in the [From.From.GetName] system has finally been completed. Although there is still much left to do, the mere completion of this metal skeleton, which has a circumference of nearly a billion kilometers, must be considered an incredible feat of engineering.\n\nWe are now ready to start work on creating the actual habitats."
CN2 utopia.2003.desc:0 "在 [From.From.GetName] 星系建造的星环世界骨架终于完成了。尽管还有很长一段路要走，仅仅是完成这个全长数十亿公里的金属骨架就已经是一项非常了不起的工程成就了。我们现在可以开始着手建造生态环境本身了。"
ADD utopia.2003.a:0 "Much work lies before us."
CN2 utopia.2003.a:0 "还有很多工作要做。"
ADD utopia.2004.name:0 "Ring World Completed"
CN2 utopia.2004.name:0 "星环世界完成"
ADD utopia.2004.desc.a:0 "Our engineers and planetary ecologists today finished the last of the habitat sections on the Ring World we built in the [completed_ringworld_system.GetName] system. The construction of this great megastructure must be considered a milestone in the history of the [Root.GetName] - we have accomplished what only a handful of civilizations in the history of our galaxy has managed before.\n\nLet this Ring World stand forever as a testament to how much the [Root.GetSpeciesName] species has achieved since we first ventured beyond the safety of our homeworld's atmosphere."
CN2 utopia.2004.desc.a:0 "今天我们的工程师们与行星生态学家们在 [completed_ringworld_system.GetName] 星系内的星环世界上完成了生态环境最终部分的建设。这个伟大巨构建筑的建造必将成为 [Root.GetName] 历史上的一块丰碑——我们达成了在银河史上只有屈指可数的少部分文明才能达成的成就。这个星环世界将永远成为 [Root.GetSpeciesName] 种族自从其离开母星的怀抱以来其成就达到了何种高度的证明。"
ADD utopia.2004.desc.b:0 "We have concluded work on the habitat sections of the Ring World we built in the [completed_ringworld_system.GetName] system. Our engineers and ecologists have accomplished the impossible yet again.\n\nThe [Root.GetName] must now truly be considered one of the greatest builders in the history of the galaxy."
CN2 utopia.2004.desc.b:0 "我们已结束了在 [completed_ringworld_system.GetName] 星系建造的星环世界的生态环境部分。我们的工程师们与行星生态学家们再次完成了不可能的任务。 [Root.GetName] 已经毫无疑问是银河史上最伟大的建筑师之一。"
ADD utopia.2004.a:0 "This is a great day."
CN2 utopia.2004.a:0 "这是伟大的一天。"
ADD utopia.2005.name:0 "[From.GetSpeciesName] Ring World"
CN2 utopia.2005.name:0 " [From.GetSpeciesName] 星环世界"
ADD utopia.2005.desc.a:0 "The [From.GetName] has accomplished what only a handful of civilizations in the history of our galaxy has managed before - they have finished construction of the colossal Ring World they were building around the primary star of the [completed_ringworld_system.GetName] system.\n\nThis technological marvel must be considered a testament to the impressive achievements of the [From.GetSpeciesName] species as a whole. They have certainly come a long way from their humble beginnings."
CN2 utopia.2005.desc.a:0 " [From.GetName] 达成了在银河史上只有屈指可数的少部分文明才能达成的成就——他们建成了围绕 [completed_ringworld_system.GetName] 星系的主星建造的巨大星环世界。这个技术奇迹将成为 [From.GetSpeciesName] 种族本身伟大成就的证明。他们从自身的卑微起源开始已经取得了很大的成就。"
ADD utopia.2005.desc.b:0 "The [From.GetName] has finished another Ring World! This massive megastructure is located in the [completed_ringworld_system.GetName] system, which is now devoid of other planetary bodies since those that once existed were dismantled and used as building material."
CN2 utopia.2005.desc.b:0 " [From.GetName] 又建成了一个星环世界！这座巨大的巨构建筑位于 [completed_ringworld_system.GetName] 星系，该星系已没有任何行星，因其原有的行星已被拆解为建造原料。"
ADD utopia.2005.a:0 "Perhaps we should consider building more as well."
CN2 utopia.2005.a:0 "或许我们也该多造点。"
ADD utopia.2005.b:0 "Another one? Is there no limit to their resources?"
CN2 utopia.2005.b:0 "又一个？他们到底有多少资源？"
ADD utopia.4000.name:0 "Dyson Sphere Construction"
CN2 utopia.4000.name:0 "戴森球建设"
ADD utopia.4000.desc:0 "Harnessing the power of the stars has been a dream of [Root.GetAdj] engineers throughout history - from crude combustion to the pale imitation of solar fusion - and we now stand ready to realize this dream. In the [From.From.GetName] system sits the scaffold upon which we will build a Dyson Sphere, encompassing [From.From.GetName] and monopolizing the cataclysmic power of the star."
CN2 utopia.4000.desc:0 "驾奴恒星的力量是 [Root.GetAdj] 工程师长久以来的夙愿——从原始的燃烧到对恒星聚变的拙劣模仿——如今我们终于能够实现此梦想了。在 [From.From.GetName] 星系中坐落着搭建戴森球的脚手架，它围绕着 [From.From.GetName] 而建，一旦完成就可以垄断来自恒星的洪荒之力。"
ADD utopia.4000.a:0 "Boundless."
CN2 utopia.4000.a:0 "无穷无尽。"
ADD utopia.4002.name:0 "Alien Megastructure"
CN2 utopia.4002.name:0 "外星巨构建筑"
ADD utopia.4002.desc.a:0 "Frenetic activity in the [dyson_system.GetName] system betrays the construction of a §HDyson Sphere§! by the [From.GetName].\n\nStill in its early stages, the completed sphere will eventually blot out the light of [dyson_system.GetName], its radiance diverted to [From.GetAdj] energy stores."
CN2 utopia.4002.desc.a:0 " [dyson_system.GetName] 星系中的疯狂行为暴露了由 [From.GetName] 发起的§H戴森球§!建设行动。该工程仍处于初级阶段，完工后的球体最终将遮蔽 [dyson_system.GetName] 的光芒，其光能和热能将被转化为 [From.GetAdj] 的能源储存。"
ADD utopia.4002.desc.b:0 "By all accounts, the [dyson_system.GetName] will soon play host to yet another Dyson Sphere operated by the [From.GetName]. Though it will take some time, the megastructure will completely envelop the system's primary star once completed."
CN2 utopia.4002.desc.b:0 "据说 [dyson_system.GetName] 即将迎来由 [From.GetName] 所修建的又一个戴森球。尽管会很耗时间，但是完工后的该巨构建筑最终将完全笼罩该星系的恒星。"
ADD utopia.4002.a:0 "All stellar powers must eventually tame the stars."
CN2 utopia.4002.a:0 "所有星际帝国最终都会征服群星。"
ADD utopia.4002.b:0 "The galaxy darkens."
CN2 utopia.4002.b:0 "星河黯淡了。"
ADD utopia.4003.name:0 "Dyson Sphere Frame"
CN2 utopia.4003.name:0 "戴森球框架"
ADD utopia.4003.desc:0 "With the frame now in place, the awesome scale of the project is evident to all.\n\n[From.From.GetName] burns in a spindly cage, but will eventually be completely surrounded by [Root.GetAdj] solar panels."
CN2 utopia.4003.desc:0 "框架现已就绪，这个规模宏大的项目已经昭然欲揭。 [From.From.GetName] 在一个纤弱的牢笼中继续燃烧，但最终将被 [Root.GetAdj] 的无数恒星能板彻底包围。"
ADD utopia.4003.a:0 "Exquisite."
CN2 utopia.4003.a:0 "精妙绝伦。"
ADD utopia.4004.name:0 "Dyson Sphere Panels Installed"
CN2 utopia.4004.name:0 "戴森球面板已安装"
ADD utopia.4004.desc:0 "While not yet complete, with the installation of advanced solar harvesters we have begun to reap the benefits of the Dyson Sphere being built in the [From.From.GetName] system.\n\nThe energy gains will only continue to increase as construction continues, eventually reaching full operational capacity when the Sphere is completed."
CN2 utopia.4004.desc:0 "尽管 [From.From.GetName] 星系中的戴森球尚未竣工，我们已经能够从目前安装的先进恒星能收获装置中获得收益了。随着建设进行，能源收益只会持续增加，最终在球体竣工后将开启完全运转能力。"
ADD utopia.4004.a:0 "Excellent."
CN2 utopia.4004.a:0 "棒极了。"
ADD utopia.4005.name:0 "[From.From.GetName] Dyson Sphere Completed"
CN2 utopia.4005.name:0 " [From.From.GetName] 戴森球已完工"
ADD utopia.4005.desc:0 "The [From.From.GetName] system's primary has now been completely enveloped by a [Root.GetAdj] Dyson Sphere.\n\nOur engineers celebrate this as a great victory, and rightly so. We have achieved what only a handful of star empires in the history of the galaxy dared imagine - the total subjugation of a star."
CN2 utopia.4005.desc:0 " [From.From.GetName] 的主星如今已经被 [Root.GetAdj] 戴森球完全包围。我们的工程师将此成就视为一项伟大的胜利并为之庆祝，而事实的确如此。我们实现了这片星河历史中极少数的帝国才敢去想像的事——也就是完全征服一颗恒星。"
ADD utopia.4005.a:0 "Energy output nominal."
CN2 utopia.4005.a:0 "能源产量微不足道。"
ADD utopia.4010.name:0 "Alien Megastructure Completed"
CN2 utopia.4010.name:0 "外星巨构建筑已完工"
ADD utopia.4010.desc:0 "The last detectable traces of light from the [From.From.From.GetName] system's star flicker out. The [From.GetName] has completed its Dyson Sphere, and a new void in the sky stands testament to [From.GetAdj] ingenuity and wealth."
CN2 utopia.4010.desc:0 "来自 [From.From.From.GetName] 星系的最后一道肉眼可见的光线熄灭了。 [From.GetName] 已经完成了戴森球，天空中的留白成为了 [From.GetAdj] 才智与财富的证明。"
ADD utopia.4100.name:0 "Sentry Array Construction"
CN2 utopia.4100.name:0 "哨卫阵列建设"
ADD utopia.4100.desc:0 "The light of suns blinds and the darkness of the void hides; only when we learned to travel faster than light did we learn just how little the light reveals.\n\nToday, we begin to end this amaurosis of ours. The Sentry Array we prepare to build in the [From.solar_system.GetName] system will one day become a stalwart panopticon, our eye on every star."
CN2 utopia.4100.desc:0 "恒星闪耀致人盲目，虚空幽暗行迹难寻；唯有掌握超光速旅行之后我们才能明白光所揭示出来的只不过是冰山一角。今天，我们将不再在无知的黑暗中蹒跚。我们准备在 [From.solar_system.GetName] 建造的哨卫阵列终有一日会成为一个坚不可摧的透视镜，每一颗星都将处于我们眼底。"
ADD utopia.4100.a:0 "All-seeing."
CN2 utopia.4100.a:0 "无所不见。"
ADD utopia.4102.name:0 "$utopia.4002.name$"
CN2 utopia.4102.name:0 "$utopia.4002.name$"
ADD utopia.4102.desc:0 "Word has reached us that the [From.GetName] has begun the construction of a vast, long-range sensor array in the [spy_system.GetName] system. While still in its early stages, the completed array is set to give them unfettered insight into interstellar travel in this galaxy."
CN2 utopia.4102.desc:0 "我们听说 [From.GetName] 开始着手在 [spy_system.GetName] 建造一个范围巨大的传感器阵列。尽管尚处于初级阶段，已完工的部分已经让他们在星际旅行领域获得了深刻的理解。"
ADD utopia.4103.name:0 "Sentry Array Hub Assembled"
CN2 utopia.4103.name:0 "哨卫阵列中心已装配"
ADD utopia.4103.desc:0 "The hub of the Sentry Array is a state-of-the-art installation in its own right, half listening post and half space telescope.\n\nHowever, it marks but the first milestone in this grand undertaking."
CN2 utopia.4103.desc:0 "哨卫阵列中心的建设堪称黑科技，将监听站和太空望远镜合二为一。然而这只不过是一个宏伟计划的第一个里程碑。"
ADD utopia.4104.name:0 "Sentry Array Completed"
CN2 utopia.4104.name:0 "哨卫阵列已完工"
ADD utopia.4104.desc:0 "Exactly what technology is housed in the ring that encircles the Sentry Array is a closely guarded secret.\n\nThe results, however, are undeniable. We now have virtually perfect knowledge of all fleet movements in the galaxy."
CN2 utopia.4104.desc:0 "环绕哨卫阵列的圆环建筑到底蕴藏着什么黑科技？这仍然是一个被严格保守的秘密。然而它所带来的成果是毋庸置疑的。我们如今对于星河之中所有舰队的动向都已了如指掌。"
ADD utopia.4104.a:0 "Well secluded, I see all."
CN2 utopia.4104.a:0 "我们窥察一切，不留踪迹。"
ADD utopia.4104.a.tooltip:0 "Activates galaxy-wide sensor range."
CN2 utopia.4104.a.tooltip:0 "将传感器范围设为全星系。"
ADD utopia.4110.name:0 "$utopia.4010.name$"
CN2 utopia.4110.name:0 "$utopia.4010.name$"
ADD utopia.4110.desc:0 "We have received word that the [From.GetName] have completed their Sentry Array in the [From.From.solar_system.GetName] system.\n\nWe should assume that they now have virtually perfect intel pertaining to the location and make-up of our fleets."
CN2 utopia.4110.desc:0 "我们得知 [From.GetName] 已经在 [From.From.solar_system.GetName] 星系完成了哨卫阵列建设。我们可以断定他们现在已经对我们舰队的位置以及构成了如指掌。"
